      cosTime User's Guide</fo:block>
    <fo:block font-size="1em" space-after="0.5em" space-before="0.5em" text-align="justify">The <fo:inline font-weight="bold">cosTime</fo:inline> application is an Erlang implementation of the OMG
      CORBA Time and TimerEvent Services.</fo:block>
  <fo:block id="idp447792" font-family="DejaVuSans, sans-serif" font-size="1.5em" font-weight="normal" keep-with-next.within-page="always" space-after="0.3em" space-before="1em"><fo:marker marker-class-name="chapter-title">1.1  The cosTime Application</fo:marker>1.1  The cosTime Application</fo:block><fo:block id="idp503504" font-family="DejaVuSans, sans-serif" font-size="1.33em" font-weight="normal" keep-with-next.within-page="always" space-after="0.3em" space-before="0.8em">1.1.1 
